Package: SpatialBall
Type: Package
Title: Spatial NBA visualization and analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Derek", "Corcoran", email = "dere.corcoran.barrios@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Derek Corcoran <derek.corcoran.barrios@gmail.com>
Description: The Spatialball package was built for the creation 
    of offensive and defensive shot charts for teams, players 
    and seasons, and more comprehensively for spatial analysis 
    of NBA data.
    For more detailed analysis please contact the maintainer.
URL: https://derek-corcoran-barrios.github.io/SpatialBall.html
